1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:04,500
<b>BREAKING NEWS:</b> Local filmmaker
discovers subtitle converter

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,800
<i>Reporter:</i> Can you tell us what happened?

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:13,000
<b>Alex:</b> I was drowning in subtitle formats.
SRT, VTT, ASS, SBV - <i>it was chaos.</i>

4
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:17,200
<i>Reporter:</i> And then you found
<b>ConvertICO.com?</b>

5
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:21,500
<b>Alex:</b> Yes! It's completely <u>free</u> and works
right in the browser. No uploads needed.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:25,800
<i>Reporter:</i> Our viewers are asking -
does it really support <b>all</b> subtitle formats?

7
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:30,000
<b>Alex:</b> SRT to VTT, VTT to SRT,
and they keep adding more.

8
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:34,800
<i>Reporter:</i> <b>Remarkable.</b> Back to you
in the studio, <i>where nothing exciting
ever happens.</i>
